orporated into recent health legislation other key features of the health care reform bill that are intended to control costs and whether they will succeed or limit care cost effectiveness research and health care reform interview with alan garber stanford university by populationreferencebureau search chp search within everything courses events fellowships news op eds people publications research other pages news of interest alan garber named provost of harvard april 15 2011 fsi stanford chp pcor news in new england journal commentary shp director alan garber explores the role of fda in regulating devices march 24 2010 announcement director alan garber discusses comparative effectiveness research at brookings event december 2 2009 announcement alan garber receives career achievement award from society for medical decision making november 11 2009 news director alan garber discusses patient care in nyt magazine article making health care better in the news new york times on november 8 2009 alan garber discusses tiered co payment findings in wall street journal article december 5 2003 in the news support map & directions contact rss+ rss xml feeds freeman spogli institute for international studies encina hall 616 serra st stanford ca 94305 6055 tel 650 736 0815 fax 650 725 2592 mail code 6055
